00:43:55.710 --> 00:43:58.150
&gt;&gt;Man's voice in audience: Did you get the
cork out?

00:43:58.150 --> 00:43:59.150
&gt;&gt;Jerry Holkins: Oh, yeah.

00:43:59.150 --> 00:44:00.150
[laughter]

00:44:00.150 --> 00:44:03.450
Just long pulls on the, yeah, and then, wax.

00:44:03.450 --> 00:44:11.650
&gt;&gt;Man's voice in audience: You probably have
a good finger on the pulse of the industry.

00:44:11.650 --> 00:44:15.770
Where do you think, yeah, what do you think
about the supposed death of-- PC gaming and

00:44:15.770 --> 00:44:16.770
sequel of it is--

00:44:16.770 --> 00:44:17.770
&gt;&gt;Mike Krahulik: Supposed is probably a good
prefix.

00:44:17.770 --> 00:44:19.470
&gt;&gt;Man's voice in audience: The, yes, Steve
says otherwise, but the, you know how they

00:44:19.470 --> 00:44:22.160
have to make these big blockbusters and some
