00:49:15.630 --> 00:49:18.069
they just want to feel like they are doing
something. Like it's somebody's job there

00:49:18.069 --> 00:49:24.299
to do something and unfortunately there are
very few options for them to appear pro-active.

00:49:24.299 --> 00:49:30.609
Except for to inconvenience me. That's more
or less the policy, I think.

00:49:30.609 --> 00:49:31.609
[pause]

00:49:31.609 --> 00:49:34.460
Is that the correct answer? I hope so. I hate
DRM.

00:49:34.460 --> 00:49:35.460
[laughter]

