&gt;&gt;Jerry Holkins: They can't have audio.

00:50:07.460 --> 00:50:08.460
&gt;&gt;Man's voice in audience: Okay.

00:50:08.460 --> 00:50:10.170
&gt;&gt;Jerry Holkins: So a long time ago, I mean
